parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS system can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: ABS warning lights illuminate
grinding noise in the brake pedal
brake pedal goes to the floor
vehicle takes longer to stop
or fails to stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The accelerator pedal sticking can cause the vehicle to accelerate unexpectedly, leading to loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: Accelerator pedal becomes stuck to the floor
vehicle speed increases uncontrollably.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine overheating can cause the engine to fail, leading to stalling or loss of power.
symptoms: Temperature light appears on the dashboard
engine stalls
or fails to restart.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbags fail to deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to shift into gear unexpectedly, leading to accidents or loss of control, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle shifts into gear without the driver's input
the vehicle rolls or moves unexpectedly when in park
the transmission warning light illuminates on the dashboard
the vehicle experiences sudden loss of power or stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the automatic interlock system can cause the vehicle to move unexpectedly, leading to accidents or loss of control, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle moves or rolls unexpectedly when in park
the vehicle shifts into gear without the driver's input
the automatic interlock system fails to engage or disengage properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A transmission fire can cause damage to the vehicle and surrounding property, and can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The transmission warning light illuminates on the dashboard
smoke or flames are visible from the transmission area
the vehicle experiences sudden loss of power or stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine head gasket can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage, loss of power, and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The temperature gauge reads high
steam comes out from under the hood
the engine makes a loud noise
the vehicle overheats
fluid leaks from the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear main seal can cause oil leaks, leading to engine damage, loss of power, and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Oil leaks from the rear main seal
oil drips from the bottom of the engine.
